sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend
    participant Backend
    participant Auth
    participant Controller
    participant DB

    User->>Frontend: Click Place Order
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/orders (Bearer)
    Backend->>Auth: Validate token
    Auth-->>Backend: Authorized
    Backend->>Controller: addOrderItems
    Controller->>DB: Save order
    DB-->>Controller: Created order
    Controller-->>Backend: 201 Created
    Backend-->>Frontend: Order JSON (id)
    Frontend-->>User: Show confirmation
